title: Soul Vegetarian
typeOfFood: Vegan, American, Delivery, Take-out, Catering, Soul food
description: Quick service all-vegan restaurant. Expanded dining room. Offers a full menu that includes lunch platters, sandwiches, desserts, specialty drinks, daily specials, soy ice cream, smoothies, veggie patties, and pizza pockets, a Sunday night platter, and Sunday brunch once a month. Oct 2013 per owner no longer using honey. Half price platters and select $3 sandwiches all day Sunday.
